data.description: STOP your search and welcome to your new home in the heart of Winter Garden!  This Beautiful home boasts tasteful updates and modern finishes and is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience with a phenomenal location.    You'll love living just minutes from the vibrant and desirable Downtown Winter Garden.  You’ll be in the center of a bustling hub of entertainment, dining, and shopping. The enchanting Plant Street Market is your go-to spot for artisanal goods, delicious food, and unique gifts. Plus, the renowned West Orange Trail is a stone's throw away, making it a breeze to enjoy outdoor adventures.    Imagine cruising the charming streets in your very own golf cart, and exploring all this wonderful community has to offer.  This home has the ideal setup for you to enjoy this unique lifestyle, JUST in time for the holidays.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fantastic home, with an ideal location and all the comforts you desire. Schedule a viewing and experience the magic of Winter Garden living for yourself!
